data.description: Welcome to your dream home!   This stunning House is a true gem, boasting four spacious bedrooms and three full bathrooms. One of the bedrooms is conveniently located downstairs, making it ideal for accommodating guests or providing a private space for a mother-in-law suite. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property offers a tranquil and private retreat.     Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a beautifully remodeled kitchen that is sure to impress even the most discerning chef. With its sleek countertops, modern appliances, and ample storage space, this kitchen is as functional as it is stylish. Upstairs you will find your own movie theater! The movie screen and projector will be yours when you buy this home!
